---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description="Kakarrot — AI 产品经理的经历与原则" shell>
  <div style={{padding: "38px 30px", borderBottom: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)"}}>
    <h1 style={{fontSize: "clamp(50px,7vw,100px)", letterSpacing: "-.07em", lineHeight: .9, fontWeight: 900, margin: "0 0 8px"}}>关于</h1>
    <p style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 ui-monospace,monospace", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", margin: 0}}>Kakarrot &mdash; AI 产品经理的经历与原则</p>
  </div>

  <div style={{display: "grid", gridTemplateColumns: "1fr 1fr", borderBottom: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)"}}>
    <section style={{padding: "38px 30px", borderRight: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)"}}>
      <h2 style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 ui-monospace,monospace", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", marginBottom: "14px"}}>经历</h2>
      <p style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, margin: 0}}>
        AI 产品经理，十年互联网与教育科技经验。经历过从零到一的产品搭建，也管理过千万级用户平台。
      </p>
    </section>
    <section style={{padding: "38px 30px"}}>
      <h2 style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 ui-monospace,monospace", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", marginBottom: "14px"}}>原则</h2>
      <ul style={{listStyle: "none", padding: 0, margin: 0}}>
        <li style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, marginBottom: "8px"}}>先理解问题，再设计方案。</li>
        <li style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, marginBottom: "8px"}}>技术是手段，不是目的。</li>
        <li style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, marginBottom: "8px"}}>最好的产品是那些用户感觉不到的产品。</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div style={{display: "grid", gridTemplateColumns: "1fr 1fr"}}>
    <section style={{padding: "38px 30px", borderRight: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)"}}>
      <h2 style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 ui-monospace,monospace", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", marginBottom: "14px"}}>这个网站</h2>
      <p style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, margin: 0}}>
        基于 Astro 构建，纯静态生成。源码在 GitHub 上公开。不追踪用户，不加载外部脚本。
      </p>
    </section>
    <section style={{padding: "38px 30px"}}>
      <h2 style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 ui-monospace,monospace", color: "var(--color-text-muted)", marginBottom: "14px"}}>联系方式</h2>
      <ul style={{listStyle: "none", padding: 0, margin: 0}}>
        <li style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6, marginBottom: "8px"}}><a href="https://github.com/kakarrot0109" style={{textDecoration: "underline", textUnderlineOffset: "2px"}}>GitHub</a></li>
        <li style={{fontSize: "17px", lineHeight: 1.6}}><a href="mailto:kakarrot@kakarrot.com" style={{textDecoration: "underline", textUnderlineOffset: "2px"}}>kakarrot@kakarrot.com</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
